snippet.title: Johnny Depp vs Amber Heard trial - Day 16
snippet.description:
Today is the final day of the Johnny Depp libel case trial against News Group Newspapers at The Royal Courts of Justice in London. 
In court, Depp's team delivered their closing statements in hope of a win for the 'Pirates of the Caribbean' actor.
